fields.description: The timeout (TimeSpan) to get an HTTP response. It is the timeout to get a response, not the timeout to read response data. Default value: 00:05:00. Type: string (or Expression with resultType string), pattern: ((\d+)\.)?(\d\d):(60|([0-5][0-9])):(60|([0-5][0-9])).
fields.name: HTTPRequestTimeout

fields.description: The write behavior for the operation. Default is 'Insert'.
fields.name: WriteBehavior
